var book = {
	"name": "Thuphuan",
	"numChapters": 22,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hi thu hi Jesuh Khrih ih a phuanmi a si. A ra thleng cing dingmi thil kha a siahhlawh pawl hnenih langter dingah Pathian in a hnenih a hmuhtermi a si. Cumi cu Khrih in a vancungmi pakhat thlah tahratin a siahhlawh Johan hnenih a theihtermi a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule Johan in a hmuhmi hmuahhmuah cu a sim ṭheh. Pathian hnen ihsin a rami thuthang le Jesuh Khrih ih a langtermi thutak cu Johan in hi bangtuk in a sim.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hi cabu a siartu le profet thusimmi a theitu le hi cabu sungih a ummi a thluntu pawl cu mi lungawi an si. Ziangahtile hi thu pawl a kimnak tikcu a nai zo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Asia peng sungih a ummi kawhhran pasarih hnenah keimah Johan in thu ka lo cah: Atuih canah a ummi le a rak um zomi le hmailam khalah a um lai dingmi Pathian le a bawi tokham hmaiih a ummi thlarau pasarih le,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> rintlak a si mi thutheitu, hrin hmaisa bik a si mi Fapa, thihnak ihsin thawhtersal a si mi leilung siangpahrang pawl uktu Jesuh Khrih in zaangfahnak le daihnak lo pe hram seh. Kannih in duhdawt ih a thihnak thisen thawngin kan sualnak ihsin in luatter zo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Puithiam bangin a siangpahrang uknak sungah Pathian le a Pa riantu si dingah kannih cu in tuah zo. Curuangah sunlawinak le huham cu Jesuh Khrih hnenah kumkhua in um ko seh. Amen.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Zoh uh! Khrih cu mero thawn a ra ding ih mi hmuahhmuah in an hmu ding; amah a suntu pawl khal in an hmu ding. Leilung tlun minung hmuahhmuah an ṭap-ai ding. Cutiin a si hrimhrim ding. Amen.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bawipa Pathian in, “Keimah cu Alfa le Omega ka si,” a ti; Amah cu atuih a ummi le a rak um zomi le hmailam khalah a um lai dingmi Ziangkimtithei a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Keimah cu nan unau Johan, Jesuh a thluntu ka si ih Khrih uknak sungih a telmi pawl parih a rathlengmi harsatnak nan tuarmi khal a tuar vemi ka si. Pathian thu le Jesuh ih phuanmi thutak ka sim ruangah Patmos tikulh ah in ret.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bawipa Ni ah Thlarau in i zeel ih ka dunglam ihsin tawtawrawt vekin a ring zetmi aw thawm ka thei.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Na hmuhmi hi ca sungah ngan awla Efesa, Smarna, Pergamum, Thiatira, Sardis, Filadelfia le Laodisia khua pasarih ih a ummi kawhhran pasarih hnenah kuat aw,” tiah i ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cutiih i titu cu zoso a si tiah ka her ih ka zoh tikah sui meisa vannak tung pasarih ka hmu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cuih meisa vannak tung pasarih lakah milai a bang zetmi pakhat a ding ih a kebeu tiang angki fual hrukin sui ṭaangkap a ṭaangah a kap ka hmu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> A sam cu tuuhmul le vur bangtuk in a rang. A mit cu meiling bangin a vaam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A ke cu somei sungih an thianter hnuah an hnawtfaimi dar vekin a tle. A aw cu tipilian tlasuar thawm bangtuk a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> A vorhlam kut in arsi pasarih a keng ih a ka sung ihsin kaphnih hriam ralnam pakhat a suak. A mithmai cu sun laitakih ni bangin a tleu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cutiin ka hmuh tikah mithi bangin a kehram ah ka ril. A vorhlam kut in i run tham ih, “Ṭih hlah aw! Keimah cu a hmaisa bik le a neta bik ka si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A nungmi khal ka si. Ka rak thi naón atu-ah kumkhua hrangin ka nung sal zo. Thihnak le mithi khua tlunah thuneitu ka si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Curuangah na hmuhmi thil pawl, atuih a ummi le hmailamih a um lai dingmi thil pawl hi ngan aw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ka vorhlam kutih na hmuhmi arsi pasarih le sui mei vannak tung pasarih ih tican thuthup cu hi bangtuk in a si. Arsi pasarih cu kawhhran pasarih ih vancungmi an si ih mei vannak tung pasarih cu kawhhran pasarih an si,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Efesa kawhhran ih vancungmi hnenah hiti in ngan aw: A vorhlam kutah arsi pasarih kengin sui mei vannak tung pasarih lakih a tawivak rerotu ih thucahmi cu hi bangtuk in a si:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na hnaṭuanmi ka thei; taima zetih hna na ṭuan zia le thinsau zetih na um zia khal ka thei. Cun miṭha lo pawl na zawi-eet thei lo zia le dungthluntu si lo cingih dungthluntu ka si a titu pawl na hniksak ih thuphanper an si zia na hmuhsuahnak thu pawl ka thei ṭheh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na thin a sau ih keimah ih ruangah na tuar; asinain na bei a dong lo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sikhalsehla mawhthluk ding pakhat ka lo nei: a hramthokih duhdawtnak na neihmi kha na nei nawn lo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na tlaknak a san zia hi ruathnik. Na sual sir awla a hmaisaih na tuahmi kha tuah sal aw. Na sualnak na tlansan lo a si ahcun ka ra ding ih na mei vannak tung hmun dangah ka ṭhawn ding.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Asinain porhtlak na sinak pakhat a um. Nikolas a thluntu pawl ih hnaṭuannak cu keimah ih ka huat tlukin na hua ve a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile Thlarau in kawhhran hnenih a simmi hi ngai uh. “Nehtu a si mi hnenah Pathian Hmuan sungih a khomi nunnak thingrah ei theinak thu ka pe ding,” a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Smarna kawhhran ih vancungmi hnenah hiti in ngan aw: a hmaisa bik le a neta bik a si mi, a thi ih a nung salmi ih thucahmi cu hi bangtuk in a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Harsatnak na tuarmi pawl ka thei. Mifarah na si khal ka thei: sikhalsehla na lian a si. Judah mi kan si an ti naón a si ngaingai lomi pawl ih an lo relsiatnak ka thei. Annih cu Satan ta an si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Harsatnak na tuar dingmi kha zianghman ṭih hlah. Ngaihnik! Satan in a lo hniksak ding ih ṭhenkhat cu thawngah thlak nan si ding. Cule nan harsatnak cu nihra a rei ding. Thihnak tuar ding a si hmanah ka hrangah rinsan tlak in um uhla nan neh man ah nunnak suilukhuh ka lo pe ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile Thlarau in kawhhran hnenih a simmi hi ngai uh. “Nehtu pawl cu voihnih thihnak in a siatsuah lo ding,” a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Pergamum kawhhran ih vancungmi hnenah hiti in ngan aw: ralnam kaphnih hriam a neituih thucahmi cu hi bangtuk in a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na umnak hmun cu ka thei: Satan in a bawi tokham a retnak hmunah a si. Ka hrangah rintlak in na nung ih Satan umnak hmunah rintlak ka thu theitu Antipas an thah lai hmanah ka parih rinsannak na neihmi cu na ṭhin cuang lo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sikhalsehla na parah lungkim lonak malte ka nei: nanmah lakah Balaam thuzirhnak a thluntu mi ṭhenkhat an um. Milem hnenih pekmi rawl einak le nupa sualtuahnak in sualnak sungih Israel mi pawl luhpi dingah Balaam in Balak kha a rak fial.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cuvek thothoin Nikolas a thluntu pawl ih thuzirhnak a pomtu khal nan lakah an um.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cuti a si ruangah hi bangtuk sualnak ihsin kir sal uh. Nan kir sal lo asile nan hnenah zamrangin ka ra ding ih cumi pawl cu ka kaa sung ihsin a suakmi ralnam thawn ka do ding a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile Thlarau in kawhhran hnenih a sim mi hi ngai uh. “Nehtu pawl cu thuh-mi Manna sang ṭhenkhat ka pe ding. Cuih tlunah lung raang pakhat fingfing in ka pe ding ih cuih lung raang parah cun a cotu lawngih theihmi an hmin thar ngan in a um fingfing ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Thiatira kawhhran ih vancungmi hnenah hiti in ngan aw: a mit meisa bangin a alh-mi le a ke cu hnawtfaimi daar vekin a tleumi Pathian Fapa ih thucahmi cu hi bangtuk in a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na hnaṭuanmi ka thei. Duhdawtnak na neih zia, rinsantlak na si zia, hna na ṭuan zia le thinsaunak na neih zia ka thei ṭheh. A hmaisa hnakin atu-ah tam sawn in hna na ṭuan ti khal ka thei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Asinain ka lo mawhthluknak pakhat a um: Pathian ih thlahmi profet ka si a ti awtu nunau Jezebel na zawi-eet theinak hi a si. Jezebel in ka minung pawl a hruaisual ruangah nupa sualnak an tuah ih milem hnenih pekmi rawl tla an ei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Thinlung sir awknak tikcu ka pek, asinain a nunsualnak lamzin ihsin a kir duh lo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Curuangah natnak thawn ihkhun ah ka thlenter ding ih nupa sualnak a tuahpitu pawl thawn tuksumza harsatnak an tuar ding. Amah thawn an tuahmi sualnak ihsin an sir awk lo ahcun hi tuarnak pawl hi atu rori-ah an parah ka thlenter ding.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Amah a thluntu pawl khal ka that ding ih cuticun kawhhran hmuahhmuah in minung ruahnak le tumtahmi a thei ṭhehtu ka si zia hi an thei ding. Cule zozo khal nan tuahmi vekin a man nan ngah ding.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Sikhalsehla Thiatira khua ih a ummi midang pawl cun hi zirhnak ṭha lo hi nan thlun lo ih midang in, ‘A thukmi Satan thuthup,’ an timi cu nan thei lo. Nan hnenih ka sim duhmi cu: nan parah thilrit bet ka tum lo;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> nan pom ciami hi ka rat hlan tiang thlah hlah uh, tihi a si.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nehtu pawl le tuah hai seh tiih ka duhmi a net tiang a tuahtu pawl cu ka Pa hnen ihsin ka ngahmi thuneihnak kha an hnenah ka pe ve ding. Miphun dangdang tlunih uknak thu an hnenah ka pe ding; thirfung thawn uk theinak le tlak beel khuai bangih miphun dang pawl khuaiparh theinak thu an hnenah ka pe ding. Cun deirel arsi khal ka pe ding.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile Thlarau in kawhhran pawl hnenih a sim mi hi ngai uh,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Sardis kawhhran ih vancungmi hnenah hiti in ngan aw: “Pathian ih thlarau pasarih le arsi pasarih a neituih thucahmi cu hi bangtuk in a si. Na hnaṭuanmi ka thei; a nungmi kawhhran tiah na hmin a thangzet naón na thi a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Curuangah ṭhangharh awla na neih hrihmi kha a thih ngah hlanah thazaang a thar in la sal aw. Ziangahtile hna na ṭuan ciami hi Pathian hmaiah an famkim hrih lo tiin ka hmu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Curuangah an lo zirhmi le na theih ciami pawl kha hngilh hlah aw; a thlun tum awla na sualnak ihsin kir sal aw. Na ṭhangharh lo a si ahcun rukru bangin na hnenah ka ra ding ih ka rat tikcu hman na thei lo ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sikhalsehla Sardis khua ih a ummi lakah mi malte cun nan hnipuan thiangfai zetin nan re a si. Puan rang hrukin keimah thawn nan feh ding, ziangahtile cutiih feh tlak nan si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nehtu pawl cu cubangtuk in puan rang an hruk ding ih nunnak cabu sung ihsin an hmin ka phiat lo ding. Ka Pa le a vancungmi pawl hmaiah ‘Ka ta an si,’ tiah langhngan in ka sim ding.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile Thlarau in kawhhran pawl hnenih a simmi hi ngai uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Filadelfia kawhhran ih vancungmi hnenah hiti in ngan aw: “A thianghlimmi le a dikmi-ih thucahmi cu hi bangtuk in a si. Amah cu David tawh a neitu a si ih sangka a onmi cu zohman in an khar thei lo ding; cule a kharmi cu zohman in an ong thei lo ding.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na hnaṭuanmi ka thei; na thazaang a mal ti khal ka thei. Asinain ka thuzirhmi na thlun ih ka hmaiah rinsan tlak in na um. Na hmaiah sangka ka ong ih zohman in an khar thei lo ding.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngaihnik! Judah mi kan si, an ti naón a si taktak lomi thuphanper pawl, Satan minung pawl cu na hnenah ka ratter dingih na hmaiah an kun ding. Ka lo duhdawt hi an zatein an thei ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka thupekmi bangtuk in thinsau in harsatnak na tuar thei ruangah leilungtlun mi hmuahhmuah hniksak dingah a ra thleng dingmi harsatnak sung ihsin ka lo humhim ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka ra cing ding. Nehtu na si ruangih na ngah dingmi laksawng cu zohmanih an lo lon theilonak dingah na neih ciami cu kil ṭha aw.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nehtu cu ka Pathian ih biakinn sungih ṭhuam ah ka tuah ding ih cuih biakinn cu a tlansan nawn lo ding. Ka Pathian ih hmin cu a parah ka ngan ding; Jerusalem khua thar, ka Pathian ih khawpi hmin khal a parah ka ngan ding. Cuih khawpi cu vancung ihsin ka Pathian hnenin a rung ṭum dingmi a si. Cule ka hmin thar khal a parah ka ngan ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile Thlarau in kawhhran pawl hnenih a simmi hi ngai uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Laodisia kawhhran ih vancungmi hnenah hiti in ngan aw: A hminah Amen a si mi, rinsantlak le theitudik a si ih Pathian ih siammi hmuahhmuah ih hramthawhnak a si mi-ih thucah cu hi bangtuk in a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na hnaṭuanmi ka thei. A daih khal na dai lo, a sat khal na sa fawn lo, ti ka thei. Na daih asile dai lawlaw aw, na sat asile sa lawlaw aw, ti ka duh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> A daih le dai si lo, a sat le sa si lo; a hlum fangfang na si ruangah ka ka sung ihsin ka lo khak suak ding.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nangmah cun, ‘Ka lian ih mi neinung ka si; zianghman tlaksammi ka nei lo,’ na ti aw. Sikhalsehla mizonzai le zangfakza na si zia na thei aw lo. Na farah, lawngfangkheh in na um ih na mit a caw.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Thu ka lo sim duhmi cu, sui ngaingai ka hnen ihsin lei awla cuticun na lian ding. Na thuam awknak ah hnipuan rang lei awla, ningzakza lawngfangkheh ih na um kha hup aw. Na mit hrangah mitna sii khal lei awla cuticun khua na hmu ding.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka duhdawtmi pawl cu ka kawk ih ka hrem a si. Curuangah taimak suah in um awla na sualnak sir aw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngaihnik! sangka kiangah ka ding ih ka king. Zokhal ka aw a thei ih sangka i ontu cu a innah ka lut dingih a hnenah rawl ka ei ding; cule anih khal keimah thawn a ei ve ding.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nehtu ka si zo ih atu-ah ka Pa ih bawi tokham parah ka Pa kiangih ka to vekin nehtu a si mi pawl cu ka bawi tokham parah ka kiangah to theinak thu ka pe ding.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile Thlarau in kawhhran pawl hnenih a simmi hi ngai uh,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih hnuah ka hun zoh ih langnak dang ka hmu sal ih vancungah sangka a ong awmi pakhat ka hmu. Cule a hmaisa-ih ka theihmi tawtawrawt bangtuk ih a ringmi aw kha ka thei ih, “Hi tawkah hung awla himi ṭheh in a ra thleng dingmi ka lo hmuh ding,” tiah cuih aw cun i ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule Thlarau in hmakhatte-ah i zeel. Vancung ahcun bawi tokham pakhat a um ih cuih tokham parah mi pakhat a to.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A mithmai cu a hringmi jasper lungmankhung le a senmi karnelian lungmankhung bangtuk in a tleu; a bawi tokham kiangkap cu a hringmi emerald lungmankhung bangtuk vangro in a kulh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A bawi tokham kimvelah a dang bawi tokham kul hluanli an um ih cuih tokham parah puan vaar a sinmi le suilukhuh a khumtu upa kul hluanli an to.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuih bawi tokham ihsin nimthla a kau zukzo ih khawri thawm a thang durdo. Cule bawi tokham hmaiah cun meisa vanmi pasarih a um ih, cuih meisa vanmi pasarih cu Pathian ih thlarau pasarih an si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bawi tokham hmaiah cun tikhal bangin a tlemi thlalang tifinriat bangtuk khal a um. Cuih bawi tokham kimvelah thilnung pali an um ih dunglam hmailam in mit in an khat ṭheh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Thilnung pakhatnak cu kiosa a bang; a pahnihnak cu cawcang a bang; a pathumnak cu minung mithmai a bang ih a palinak cu a zammi mupi a bang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Thilnung pali cu thla paruk ciar an nei ih cuih thla cu a sunglam a lenglam in mit in an khat ṭheh. Sun le zan cat loin hla an sak ih, Thianghlim, thianghlim, thianghlim, Ziangkimtithei Bawipa Pathian; A rak um zomi le atu-ah a ummi le hmailam khalah a umlai dingmi a si, tiah an sak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Thilnung pali in bawi tokham parah a to ih kumkhua in kumkhua tiang a nungmi hnenah sunlawinak le upatnak le lungawinak hla an sak.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cubangtuk ih hla an sak tikah bawi tokham parih a totu hmaiah cun an kun ih kumkhua in kumkhua tiang a nungmi cu an biak. An sui lukhuh cu bawi tokham hmaiah cun an ṭhum ih:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Kan Bawipa le kan Pathian, Nang cu sunlawinak le upatnak le huham co tlak na si. Ziangahtile nang cun ziang hmuahhmuah na tuah ih na thu in siam mi le nunter mi an si,” tiah an ti."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bawi tokham parih a tomi in cazual pakhat a vorhlam kut in a ken kha ka hmu. Cuih cazual cu a sunglam le lenglam in nganmi a si ih tacik pasarih ih khenmi a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule vancungmi pakhat a cak zetmi ka hmu ih aw ring zetin, “Hi tacik khenmi siatbal tahratin cazual ong dingah a tlakmi zoso a um?” tiah a au.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Asinain cuih cazual ong tahratin a sung a zoh theitu vancungah siseh, leitlunah siseh, leihnuai khalah siseh, zohman an um lo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cutiin cazual a ongtu ding tlak le a sung a zohtu ding tlak zohman an um lo ka hmuh tikah napiin ka ṭap.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cutikah upa pakhat in, “Ṭap hlah. Zohhnik! Judah phun sung ihsin a rami Kiosa tiih kawhmi, David ih tefa misunglawi tiih kawhmi cu nehtu a si zo ih tacik pasarih cu a siatter dingih cazual cu a ong ding,” tiah i ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule Tuufa pakhat, bawi tokham laifangah a ding ih thilnung pali le upa pawl in an kulh kha ka hmu. Cuih Tuufa cu thah ciami a bang. Ki pasarih le mit pasarih a nei ih cuih mit pasarih cu leilung tlun khuazakip ah a thlahmi Pathian ih thlarau pasarih an si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tuufa cu a va feh ih bawi tokham parih a tomi-ih vorhlam kut ihsin cazual cu a lak.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cutiih a lak ṭheh vete in Tuufa hmaiah cun thilnung pali le upa kul hluanli cu an bok. Ṭingṭang pakhat ciar le rimhmui in a khat mi sui kheng pakhat fingfing an keng ih cuih rimhmui cu Pathian minung pawl ih thlacamnak a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hla thar an sak ih: “Nangmah cu cazual latu dingah le tacik phoihtu dingah na tlak a si. Ziangahtile thahnak na tuar zo ih, na thihnak thawngin phunkip hnamkip le ṭongtin hrintin ihsin Mi tampi Pathian hrangah na lei zo a si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kan Pathian riantu dingah puithiam phun le siangpahrang uknak ah annih cu na tuah zo ih annih in lei tlun an uk ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka zoh sal tikah a thawng sawm a thawng za, a siar ih siar cawk lo vancungmi pawl ih aw thawng ka thei. Bawi tokham le thilnung pali le upa pawl ih kimvelah an ding ih,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ring zetin hla an sak ih: “Thah a tuartu Tuufa cu huham le lennak, fimnak le cahnak, Hminthannak le sunlawinak le thangṭhatnak co tlak a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule vancungah siseh, leitlun le leihnuai khalah siseh, ti sungih a ummi khal in siseh, lei le van ih nunnak thaw a neimi hmuahhmuah in: “Bawi tokham ih a totu le Tuufa hnenah thangṭhatnak le upatnak, Sunlawinak le cahnak cu a kumkhua in um ko seh,” tiah hla an sak.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule thilnung pali in, “Amen,” an ti tikah Upa pawl cun an bok ih an biak."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule Tuufa in tacik pasarih lakah pakhat a phoih kha ka hmu ih thilnung pali lakih pakhat in, a aw khuari thawm bangin, “Ra,” tiah a ti ka thei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka zoh ih rang raang pakhat ka hmu. A parih a totu cun li pakhat a keng ih bawi lukhuh khal an pek. Mi nehtu in neh dingih a feh bangin a feh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cule Tuufa in tacik pahnihnak a phoih ih thilnung pahnihnak in, “Ra,” a ti kha ka thei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Rang dang pakhat a ra suak ih rang sen a si. A parih a totu hnenah leilung tlunah pakhat le pakhat thah awknak ral thok dingin thu an pek. Ralnam tumpi khal an pek.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule Tuufa in tacik pathumnak a phoih ih thilnung pathumnak in, “Ra,” a ti kha ka thei. Ka zoh ih rang dum pakhat ka hmu. A parih a totu in cuai thlainak zaazu pakhat a kut in a keng.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Thilnung pali lak ihsin aw bangtuk thawng ka thei ih, “Nikhat hlawhman ah sangvut pawng khat, ni khat hlawh manah barli pawng thum. Asinain olif thingkung le sabit hmuan cu siatsuah hlah,” a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule Tuufa in tacik palinak a phoih ih thilnung palinak in, “Ra,” a ti kha ka thei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka zoh ih rang a tisa a raammi pakhat ka hmu. A parih a totu cu a hminah Thihnak a si ih Hell in a dunglam naihte ihsin a thlun. Anmah tla cu leilung mi ih ṭhenli ṭhenkhat kha raldonak, paamnak, natnak le sahrang ih tuahmawhnak in thah dingah thu pekmi an si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule Tuufa in tacik panganak a phoih. Pathian thu an sim ruangah le rintlak zetin an phuan ngam ruangih thah a tongtu pawl ih thlarau cu biakṭheng hnuai ah ka hmu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ring zetin an au ih, “A thianghlimmi le a dikmi Cungnungbik Bawipa, leilung tlun minung kan thisen a luantertu pawl hi ziangtik tiangso phuba la lo le hrem loin na zuah ding?” an ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Annih pawl cu puan rang pakhat ciar pek an si ih, “Nanmah bangin thah a tuar dingmi nan unau le nan siahhlawhpi pawl an kim hlan lo caan malte sung cawl hrih uh,” tiah an sim.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Tuufa in tacik paruknak a phoih khi ka hmu. Nasa zetin ling a hnin ih ni cu puansia dum vekin a dum ih thlapi cu thisen bangin a sen ṭheh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule arsi tla cu thlipi in theikuh a sem thlak vekin leilung ah an tla.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Van cu cazual vekin a zual aw hlo ih tlang le tikulh hmuahhmuah cu an umnak hmun ihsin an ṭhawn ṭheh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule leilung tlun siangpahrang pawl le ram uktu pawl le ralbawi pawl, milian le thuneitu pawl le midang hmuahhmuah, sal le miluat thawn, lungkua sung le tlangpar lungpuk hnuai ah an relh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tlang le lungpi pawl hnenah, “In nen uhla bawi tokham ih a totu mithmai le Tuufa thinhengnak ihsin in thup hram uh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> An thinhengnak a thlen ni, tuksumza ni a thleng zo ih zoso a tuar thei ding?” tiah an au."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih hnuah leilung kil li ah a dingmi vancungmi pali ka hmu. Cuih vancungmi pali in leilung parah le tifinriat ah le thingkung ah thlipi hrang lo dingin an kham.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nisuah lam ihsin a nungmi Pathian ih hminsinnak tacik a kengtu dang vancungmi pakhat a hung suah khi ka hmu. Pathian in leilung le tifinriat siatsuah theinak thu a pekmi vancungmi pali kha aw ring zetin a hei ko.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Vancungmi cun, “Kan Pathian ih siahhlawh pawl an cal ih hminsinnak tacik khen an si ṭheh hlan ahcun leilung le tifinriat le thingkung pawl siatsuah hrih hlah uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cule Pathian hminsinnak tacik in an cal ih khen ciami pawl cu thawng za le thawng sawmli le thawng li an si, tiah in sim. Cumi cu Israel miphun hleihnih sungin an si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Judah hrin in thawng hleihnih, Reuben hrin in thawng hleihnih, Gad hrin in thawng hleihnih,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Asher hrin in thawng hleihnih, Naftali hrin in thawng hleihnih, Manasseh hrin in thawng hleihnih,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Simeon hrin in thawng hleihnih, Levi hrin in thawng hleihnih, Issakhar hrin in thawng hleihnih,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Zebulun hrin in thawng hleihnih, Josef hrin in thawng hleihnih, Benjamin hrin in thawng hleihnih an si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cuih hnuah ka hun zoh ih mipi tamzet ka hmu; zohmanih siarcawk lo miruunpi an si. Annih cu phun kip, hnam kip, le hrin kip ṭong kip ihsin a rami an si ih bawi tokham le Tuufa hmaiah an ding; puan rang an hruk ih an kut in ṭhulhfau hnah an keng fingfing.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Rundamnak cu bawi tokham parih a totu kan Pathian le Tuufa hnen ihsin a ra,” tiah ring zetin an au.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Vancungmi hmuahhmuah cu bawi tokham le upa pawl le thilnung pali kimvelah an ding. Bawi tokham hmaiah an bok ih Pathian an biak;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Amen! Thangṭhatnak, sunlawinak, fimnak, lungawinak, upatnak, huham le cahnak cu kumkhua in kan Pathian ta si ko seh, Amen!” tiah an ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Upa kul hluanli lakih pakhat in, “Hi puan rang a sintu pawl hi zoso an si? Khuitawk in so an ra?” tiah i sut.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Bawipa, ka thei lo. Nang na thei sawn ding,” tiah ka ti. Cule anih in, “Himi pawl cu hremnak nasazet sung ihsin himdam in a ra suakmi an si. An puan cu Tuufa thisen sungah an sawp ih an vaar ter zo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Curuangah Pathian ih bawi tokham hmaiah an ding ih biakinn sungah a hnaṭuan cu a sun a zan in an ṭuan. Bawi tokham parih a totu in a umpi ding ih cuih a umpinak cu an himnak a si ding.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> An ril a rawng nawn lo ding ih an ti khal a haal nawn lo ding; ni in a ling hai lo ding ih vansaanglam thawsat khal an tuar lo ding.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ziangahtile bawi tokham laifangih a ummi Tuufa cu anmah khaaltu a si ding ih nunnak petu cerhti umnak ah a hruai hai ding. Cule an mitthli hmuahhmuah cu Pathian in a hnul sak ṭheh ding a si,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tuufa in tacik pasarihnak a phoih tikah vancungah nazi hrek sung hrawng thawthaang zianghman um loin a dai ṭhepṭhep.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule Pathian hmaiih a dingtu vancungmi pasarih kha ka hmu ih an hnenah tawtawrawt pasarih an pek.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A dang vancungmi pakhat, rimhmui urnak kheng a kengtu, a ra ih biakṭheng kiangah a ding. Pathian minung pawl ih thlacamnak thawn pek cih dingah le bawi tokham hmaiih a dingmi sui biakṭheng parih pe dingah cuih vancungmi hnenah cun rimhmui tampi an pek.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Pathian hmaiih a dingtu vancungmi ih kut ihsin rimhmui urnak meikhu cu Pathian minung pawl ih thlacamnak thawn an kai tlaang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule vancungmi in rimhmui urnak kheng cu a lak ih biakṭheng ih meisa vaam thawn a khahter hnuah leilungah a hlon. Cuvete in khua a ri, ṭeek a tla, nimthla a kau ih ling a hnin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule vancungmi pasarih cu an tawtawrawt pasarih tum dingah an tiar aw cia.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Vancungmi pakhatnak in a tawtawrawt cu a tum ih thisen thawn a rawi awmi rial le meisa cu leilung ah ruah bangin a sur ciamco. Leilung ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat a kang ṭheh, thingkung ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat a kang ṭheh ih hrampi hring cu a zatein an kang ṭheh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Vancungmi pahnihnak in a tawtawrawt a tum ih a alh hluahhlomi meitlang tumpi vek thil pakhat khi tifinriat sungah an vun hlon. Cutikah tifinriat ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat cu thisen ah a cang ṭheh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tifinriat sung thilnung ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat an thi ih tangphawlawng ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat an siat ṭheh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Vancungmi pathumnak in a tawtawrawt a tum. Meifar bangin a alh hluahhlomi arsi tumpi pakhat cu van ihsin tiva le cerhti pawl ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat parah a tla.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cuih arsi hmin cu, “A Kha,” ti a si. Tidai ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat cu tikha ah a cang ih cutiih a khaat ruangah cuih ti a intu mi tampi an thi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule vancungmi palinak in a tawtawrawt a tum ih ni ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat, thlapi ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat le arsi pawl ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat cu an siat ṭheh. Curuangah an tleunak ṭhenthum ih ṭhenkhat cu a hlo. Sun ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat ah siseh, zan ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat ah siseh, tleunak a um lo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule ka hun zoh ih vansangpi-ah khin mupi pakhat a zam ih, “Ṭihnungza! Ṭihnungza! Vancungmi pathum in an tawtawrawt an tum tikah cun leilung parih a ummi hmuahhmuah hrangah ṭihnungza a va si so!” tiah ring zetin a ti ka thei."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule vancungmi panganak in a tawtawrawt a tum ih van ihsin leilungah arsi pakhat a tlak ka hmu. Cule cuih arsi cu tawpneilo khurih tawhfung a hnenah an pek.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cuih arsi in tawpneilo khur cu a on tikah sosernak somei tumpi ihsin meikhu a suah vekin meikhu a hung suak luailo. Cuih meikhu in ni tleunak le thli lak khal a thimter ṭheh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kharbok tampi cu cuih meikhu lak ihsin leilung parah an rung tla ih varngen meipir neihmi huham vek kha an hnenah pek an si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuih kharbok pawl cu hrampi, thingkung le a dang hramkung khal siseh, siatsuah lo dingin an sim. An siatsuah theimi cu an cal ah Pathian hminsinnak tacik a nei lomi lawng an si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hi minung pawl thah theinak thu an nei lo; thla nga sung hrem theinak thu lawng an nei. Mi an hrem tikih a nat zia cu varngen meipir in mi a hen ih a nat bangtuk khi a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cuih thla nga sungah cun minung in thihnak an hawl rero ding naón an tong lo ding; thih an duh ding naón thihnak in a tlansan ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cuih kharbok pawl cu raldo dingih a ralringmi rang bangtuk an si. An lu parah sui lukhuh a bangmi an khum; an hmai cu minung hmai an bang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> An lu-ih sam cu nunau sam bangtuk a si; an ha tla cu kiosa ha bangtuk a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> An ṭaang cu raldonak ih tuahmi thir ṭaangphaw bangtuk a si mi in an khuh ṭheh ih an thla an khawn thawm cu raldonak hmunih a tlan ciamcomi rangleng tampi awn thawm a bang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mei an nei ih varngen meipir bangin mi an hen thei; thla nga sung mi an hrem theinak khal cu an mei ih huham neihmi ruangah a si.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Anmah uktu siangpahrang an nei ih cuih an siangpahrang cu tawpneilo khur uktu vancungmi a si. A hmin cu Hebru ṭong in Abaddon a si; Grik ṭong cun Apollion a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ṭihnungza pakhatnak cu a cem; hi hnuah ṭihnungza pahnih an ra hrih ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule vancungmi paruknak in a tawtawrawt a tum. Pathian hmaiih a ummi sui biakṭheng ih kil li ihsin aw thawng ka thei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cuih aw in vancungmi paruknak hnenah, “Eufrates Tivapi kapih ṭemcih in a ummi vancungmi pali cu thlah thlang hai aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Vancungmi pali cu thlah an si ih annih cu hi nazi, hi ni, hi thla le hi kum cekci-ah minung hmuahhmuah ih ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat that ṭhehtu dingih timtuahmi an rak si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Rang ralkap pawl cu an zatein million zahnih an si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule hmuhmi ka neihnak ahcun rang le rang totu pawl ka hmu. An raldonak ṭaangphaw cu meiling bangin a sen, safaira timi lungmankhung bangin mepian a si ih kaat bangin a aihre. An rang pawl lu cu kiosa lu bangtuk an si ih an kaa sung ihsin meisa, meikhu le kaat mei-alh bangtuk an suak zukzo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuih rang ka sung ihsin a suak zukzo mi minung siatsuahtu phunthum: meisa, meikhu le kaat mei-alh in minung ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat an that ṭheh a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Rang pawl huham neihnak cu an kaa le an mei ah a si. An mei cu rul vek a si ih lu an nei; cuih an lu cu minung tuahmawhnak ah an hmang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hi minung siatsuahtu phunthum ih an thah ngah lomi minung pawl cun anmah ih tuahcopmi thil kha an tlansan cuang lo. Khawsia an biaknak, sui le ngun le daar le lungto le thing ih tuahmi, a hmu thei lo, a ṭong thei lo, a feh thei lo, an kutih tuahcopmi milem pawl an biaknak an baang cuang lo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Culawng si loin mi an thahnak, dawi an hmannak, nupa sual an tuahnak le ruk an ruknak pawl cun an sir cuang fawn lo."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule a cak zetmi vancungmi pakhat vancung ihsin a rung ṭum ka hmu. Amah cu mero in a thuam aw ih a lu kimvelah vangro a lang. A hmai cu ni bangtuk a si ih a ke cu meisa ṭhuam bangtuk a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A kut in pharh ciami cazual a keng. A vorhlam ke in tifinriat a pal ih a kehlam ke in leilung a pal;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> cule a au ih a aw rindan cu kiosa tampi aw bangtuk a si. Cutiih a au ṭheh vete in khuari pasarih in tlir durdo in an hun let.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cutiin an ṭong ṭheh vete in ca in ngan ka tum. Asinain van ihsin aw ka thei ih, “Khawri pasarih ih simmi kha thuthup ah re aw; ngan hrih hlah,” tiah i run ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule ka hmuh ciami vancungmi, tifinriat le leilungih a dingtu in van lamah a vorhlam kut a khai ih,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> kumkhua-in kumkhua tiang a nungmi Pathian, van le leilung, tipi thuanthum le a sungih ummi hmuahhmuah a tuahtu Pathian ih hmin in siatcam in thukamnak a tuah. Cutikah vancungmi in, “A rei nawn lo ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Vancungmi pasarihnak in a tawtawrawt a tum tikah a siahhlawh a si mi profet pawl hnenih a rak than ciami a thupte ih a tumtahmi cu Pathian in a kimter ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule vancung ihsin aw ka theihmi in, “Va feh awla tifinriat le leilungih a dingtu kut sungih a ummi pharh ciami cazual khi va la aw,” tiah i run ti sal.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Vancungmi hnenah cun ka va feh ih cazual fate cu ka va dil. Anih in, “La awla ei aw; na pum sungah a kha ding naón na kaa sungah cun khuaitizu bangin a thlum ding,” tiah i ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> I ti vekin cazual cu ka lak ih ka ei tikah ka kaa sungah khuaitizu vekin a thlum; asinain ka dolh tikah ka pum sungah cun a kha ngaingai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule in sim sal ih, “Pathian in miphun tampi, hrin tampi, ṭong tampi le siangpahrang tampiih thu thawn peh aw in a simmi kha na phuan sal a ṭul ding,” tiah i ti."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tahfung a bangmi funghreu pakhat i pek ih, “Va feh awla Pathian biakinn le biakṭheng va tah aw; cule biakinn sungih Pathian a biatu pawl siar aw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Asinain biakinn tual cu va tah hlah, ziangahtile Pathian thei lomi pawl hnenah pek a si zo ih cu pawl cun thla sawmli le thla hnih sung Khawpi Thiang cu an cilbal thluh ding.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> I theihpitu pahnih, buri hnipuan thawn thuam aw in, ka thlah ding; annih in Pathian thu cu profet bangin ni thawngkhat ni zahnih le sawmruk sung an sim ding,” tiah i ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuih theihpitu pahnih cu leilung Bawipa ih hmaiah a dingmi Olif thingkung pahnih le mei-inn pahnih an si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Anmah a siatsuah tumtu an ral pohpoh cu an kaa sung ihsin a suakmi meisa in an siatsuah ding; cuti cun annih tuahmawh a tumtu cu thah an si ding.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Van pihter theinak thu an nei ih Pathian thu an phuan sung cu van ihsin ruah a sur lo ding. Tidai tlun khalah thu an nei ih cerhti pawl kha thisen ah an canter thei. Leilung hi an duh tik caan pohah natnak a phunphun in hrem theinak thu an nei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> An thusim an ṭheh tikah tawpneilo khur sung ihsin a suakmi sahrang in a do ding. A neh dingih a that ding.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule an ruak cu an Bawipa thinglamtah parih an thahnak khawpi lamzin ah an taanta ding. Cuih khawpiih hmin deu cu Sodom a si lole Izipt a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Miphun kip, hrin kip, ram kip le ṭong kipih mi hmuahhmuah in an ruak cu ni thum le a hrek sung an zoh ding ih a phum ding khal an kham ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hi profet pahnih an thih ruangah leilung tlun minung cu an lung a awi ding. An lungawinak puai an tuah ding ih pakhat le pakhat laksawng an ṭhen aw ding, ziangahtile hi profet pahnih ruangah leilung mi harsatnak tamzet an rak tuar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Asinain ni thum le a hrek hnuah Pathian hnen ihsin nunnak petu thaw a ra ih an sungah a lut ih annih cu an hung ding; cumi a hmutu hmuahhmuah cu an tuk a sum ṭheh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule cuih profet pahnih cun van ihsin, “Hinah hung uh,” tiah a run titu aw ringzet an thei. An ral pawl ih mithmuh rori-ah annih cu mero thawn vancungah an kai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cuih caan cekci-ah nasazet in ling a hnin ih khawpi ṭhenhra ih ṭhenkhat a siat ṭheh; minung thawng sarih an thi. Midang pawl cu ṭih le phangin an um ih vancung Pathian ih maksak zia an hmu ih an thangṭhat.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ṭihnungza pahnihnak cu a cem, asinain pathumnak rei lote-ah a ra ding.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule a pasarihnak vancungmi in a tawtawrawt a tum ih vancungah a ring zetmi aw in, “Leilung tlun uk theinak huham cu kan Bawipa le a Messiah kut sungah a um zo ih kumkhua-in kumkhua tiang amah in a uk ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutikah Pathian hmaiah an bawi tokham ih a totu upa kul hluanli pawl cu an bok ih Pathian an biak,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Annih in, “Ziangkimtithei Bawipa Pathian, atu-ah a ummi le hlan ihsin a rak um zomi! A nasami na huham na langter ih uknak hram na thok zo ruangah kan lo thangṭhat.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na thinheng a langnak tikcu a thleng ih mithi pawl thuṭhen caan a kim ruangah, Pathian awi lo pawl an thin a ling in a ling. Na siahhlawh profet pawl le a lo upattu na minung pawl a tum a seen in ṭuanman an ngah caan a thleng a si. Leilung a siatsuahtu siatsuahnak an ton caan a thleng zo,” tiah an ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Vancung ih a ummi Pathian biakinn an ong ih cutawkah Thukam Kuang a um. Cule nimthla a kau zukzo, khua a ri durdo, ling a hnin ih rial napi in a tla."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule vanah khawruahharza thil pakhat a lang. Nunau pakhat a lang ih a thuam cu ni a si; thlapi a ke thuaiah a ret ih arsi hleihnih ih tuahmi siangpahrang lukhuh a khum.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Fa a vun ih nau hrin caan a kim. Nauhrin natih a nat ruangah a ai rero.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cule vanah a dang khawruahhar hmuhsaknak mak pakhat a lang. Rulhreng sen tumzet, lu pasarih le ki pahra a neimi a lang. A lu pawl cun siangpahrang lukhuh pakhat fingfing an khum.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A mei in vanih arsi ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat leilungah a vuak thlak. Nau nei ding nunau hmaiah a ding ih nau a suah vete in deh dingin a bawh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule cuih nunau nu in miphun hmuahhmuah thirfung thawn a uktu dingah fapa a hring. Asinain naute cu an lak ih Pathian le a bawi tokham hnenah an tlanpi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nunau cu Pathian in hmun a remsak ciami hramlakah a tlan. Cutawkah ni thawngkhat zahnih le sawmruk sung an cawm ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule vanah raldo awknak a um. Mikhael le a vancungmi pawl in rulhreng cu an do; rulhreng le a vancungmi khal in an do ve.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Asinain rulhreng cu a sun ruangah a vancungmi pawl thawn vancungah an um thei nawn lo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Rulhreng tumpi, khuahlan rulpi, Khawsia a si lole Satan tiih kawh mi, leilung pumpuluk mibumtu cu van ihsin an hlon. A vancungmi pawl thawn leilungah an vun thlak.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cule vancungah aw ringzet ka thei ih, “Pathian ih rundamnak a thleng zo! Pathian in siangpahrang a sinak a huham a langter zo! Messiah ih huham a langter zo! Ziangahtile Pathian hmaiah dingin, a sunzan in kan unau sual a puhtu cu vancung ihsin hlon a si zo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kan unau pawl in Tuufa thisen le thutak an phuanmi thawngin nehnak an ngah zo. An nunnak an pe siang ih thih khal an ngam a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Curuangah vancung le vanih a ummi hmuahhmuah nan lungawi uh! Asinain leilung le tifinriat hrangah cun an hmakhua a va pit so! Ziangahtile Satan nan hnen a rung thleng zo ih, Caan reipi a nei nawn lo ti a theih ruangah a thin a heng ngaingai,” tiah a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Rulhreng in leilungah in thlak ti a theih vete in fapa a hringtu nunau cu dawi a thok.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Asinain nunau nu cu a hrangah rem ciami hramlakih zuannak dingah a tum zetmi mupiih thla pahnih an pek. Cutawkah rulhrengih siatsuah thei lo dingin kum thum le a hrek sung an kilkhawi ding.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule nunau nu cu tilian in fenseh tiah rulhreng in a kaa sung ihsin tidai a suahter ciamco.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Asinain nunau nu bawm dingah leilung cu a kaa a ang ih rulhreng kaa sungin a suakmi tidai cu a rak dolh ṭheh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Rulhreng cu nunau nu parah a thin a heng tuk ih nunau tefa pawl Pathian thukham a thluntu le Jesuh ih phuanmi thutak a rinsantu hmuahhmuah do dingah a pok lala.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutiin tifinriat kapah rulhreng cu a ding."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule tifinriat sung ihsin sahrang a hung suak ka hmu. Ki pahra le lu pasarih a nei; a ki parah cun siangpahrang lukhuh pakhat fingfing an khum ih a lu parah Pathian hmuhsuamnak hmin pakhat fingfing an um.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cuih sahrang cu tlavang a bang; a ke cu savom ke bangtuk a si ih a kaa cu kiosa kaa bangtuk a si. Rulhreng in a neihmi a huham, a siangpahrang tokham le a thuneihnak maksak cu a pek.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sahrang ih lu pakhat cu thihpi tlak besia zetih hriammi a bang, asinain a cuih a hriamhma cu a dam. Leilung pumpuluk an mang a bang ih sahrang cu an thlun.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Rulhreng in a thuneihnak sahrang hnenih a pek ruangah mi hmuahhmuah in rulhreng cu an biak. Cule sahrang khal an biak thotho ih, “Sahrang a bangtu zoso a um? Zo in so a do thei ding?” an ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sahrang cu Pathian hmuhsuamnak le hminsiatnak thu kha puarthau zetin rel thei dingah an on ih thla sawmli le thla hnih sung thuneih theinak khal on a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cuticun Pathian le a hmin, a umnak hmun le vancungih a ummi hmuahhmuah kha sahrang cun a camriam ciamco.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cuih tlunah Pathian ih minung pawl do dingah le neh dingah caan an on ih hrin kip, ram kip, ṭong kip, le phun kip tlunah thuneihnak an pek.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cuticun leilungtlun mi hmuahhmuah in sahrang cu an bia ding; asinain leilung seem hlan ihsin nunnak cabu sungih hmin khum ciami pawl cun an bia lo ding; cuih nunnak cabu cu thah a si mi Tuufa-ih ta a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Theihnak hna nan neih asile ngai uh!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sal ih kaih ding ti ciami cu kaih an si ding ih ralnam ih thah ding ti ciami cu thah an si ko ding. Hi bangtuk caanah Pathian minung pawl in thinsau zetih tuar theinak le rintlak sinak an langter a ṭul ngaingai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule sahrang dang pakhat leilung sung ihsin a hung suah ka hmu. Cuih sahrang in tuufa ki bangtuk ki pahnih a nei ih rulhreng bangin a ṭong.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sahrang pakhatnak ih a neihmi a nasa zetmi thuneihnak kha a mithmuh rori-ah a hmang. Thihpi tlak hriamhma a pu naón a hma a dam zomi a pakhatnak sahrang cu leilung le leilung tlunih a ummi hmuahhmuah in an bia dingah a hneek ciamco hai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hi sahrang pahnihnak in a mak ngaingaimi khawruahharza an tuah. Mi hmuahhmuah ih mithmuh ah van ihsin leilungah meisa a tlakter.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule pakhatnak sahrang mithmuh rori ih khawruahharza tuah theinak thu an pek ruangah leilung tlunih a ummi minung hmuahhmuah a bum thei a si. Ralnam hriamhma a pu naón a nung thothomi sahrang upatnak ah amah ih zuklem tuah dingah thu a pek.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sahrang pakhatnak lem sungah nunnak thaw thawlut dingah sahrang pahnihnak cu thu an pek ih cuticun a lem cu a ṭong thei ih tlunah amah a bia lotu pawl kha a that ṭheh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cuih sahrang in mi hmuahhmuah, mitum siseh mite siseh, milian siseh mifarah siseh, sal siseh, miluat siseh, an vorhlam kutah a si lole an cal ah hranhram in hminsinnak a tuah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cuih hminsinnak an neih lo ahcun zianghman an zuar thei lo ih an lei thei fawn lo; cuih hminsinnak cu sahrang hmin a si lole sahrang hmin ai-ih hmanmi nambat a si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hi zawn ah hin fimnak hman a ṭulzet. Fimnak a neitu in sahrang nambat ih tican cu an tuat thei, ziangahtile cuih nambat cu mi pakhat hmin ai-ih hmanmi a si ih, a nambat cu zaruk sawmruk le paruk a si."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule ka hun zoh ih Zion Tlangah Tuufa a din ka hmu; amah thawn hmun khatah mi thawngza le thawng sawmli le thawngli an um ih cu pawl cu amah ih hmin le a Pa ih hmin an cal ih nganmi an si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule vancung ihsin aw pakhat ka thei ih cuih aw cu tilian tlasuar awn le khawri ringzet awn vek a si. Ṭingṭang tum thiammi pawl ih an ṭingṭang tum aw bangtuk khal a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Minung thawngza le thawng sawmli le thawngli pawl cu siangpahrang tokham le thilnung pali le upa pawl hmaiah an ding. Hla thar an sak ih cuih hla cu anmah lawngih zir theimi a si. Mi hmuahhmuah sung ihsin anmah lawng tlen ciami an si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Anmah cu mi thianghlim an si, nunau thawn a pawl aw dah lomi an si ih a himmi an si. Tuufa fehnak kipah an thlun. Mi hmuahhmuah lak ihsin tlenmi an si ih, thlairah hmaisa bik bangtuk in, Pathian le Tuufa hnenah hlan hmaisa bikmi an si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Thuphan an per dah lo; mawhnak zianghman an nei lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule vanah a zam reromi vancungmi pakhat ka hmu. Amah cu leilung tlun miphun kip, hrin kip, ṭong kip le ram kip hnenah kumkhua ih a hmunmi Thuthang ṭha thantu a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Aw ring zetin, “Pathian upat uhla a maksaknak thangṭhat uh! Ziangahtile miphun kip an thu rel caan a thleng zo. Van le leilung, tifinriat le cerhtiput hmuahhmuah a tuahtu kha bia uh!” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Vancungmi pahnihnak in pakhatnak cu a thlun ih, “A nasa zetmi Babilon cu a siat zo, a siat ngah zo a si. A tisa hiarnak sabitzu kha mi hmuahhmuah a pek ih, a ritter ṭheh a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Vancungmi pathumnak in a hmaiih a zammi vancungmi pahnih kha a thlun ih aw ring zetin, “Zokhal sahrang le milem a bia ih a hminsinnak a cal ah a si lo le a baan ah a neitu cu,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Pathian thinhengnak khuathai sungih thletmi a thinhengnak sabitzu hran cu a in ding. Cuih zu a intu cu vancung mithiang pawl le Tuufa hmaiah meisa le kaat mei-alh sungih hremnak an tuar ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Anmah hremnak meisa khu cu cat loin tlunah a kai ringring. Sahrang le a lem a biatu le a hmin hminsinnak a neitu hrangah cun sunah siseh zanah siseh hnangamte ih colhdamnak caan an nei nawn lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hi bangtuk caanah Pathian minung pawl, Pathian thukham a thluntu le Jesuh hrangah rintlak zetih a nungtu pawl in thinsau in tuar theinak an neihmi an langter a ṭul ngaingai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule vancung ihsin aw pakhat ka thei ih, “Himi hi ngan aw. Bawipa zum cingte ih a thitu pawl cu mi lungawi an si,” tiah a ti. Cutikah Thlarau in, “A si ngaingai! Annih cu an hnaṭuan khunghar ihsin an cawl thlang ding a si; ziangahtile an ṭuanmi in a thlun hai ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule ka hun zoh ih a raangmi mero ka hmu; cuih mero parah cun a lu ah sui-ih tuahmi siangpahrang lukhuh a khum ih a kutah a hriam zetmi favah a kengtu Milai Fapa bangtuk ka hmu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Biakinn sung ihsin vancungmi pakhat a ra suak ih mero parih a totu hnenah cun aw ring zetin, “Na favah cu fang ah-nak ah hmang aw, ziangahtile a caan a kim zo; leilung tlun rawlkhawm a cu zo,” tiah a ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule mero parih a totu in leilung tlunah a favah cu a vun hawi ih leilung tlun fang cu a khawm.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule a dang vancungmi pakhat vancung biakinn ihsin a ra suak ka hmu; anih khal a hriam zetmi favah a nei ve.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cule a dang vancungmi pakhat, meisa tlun thuneitu, biakṭheng ihsin a ra suak. Favah hriam zet a neitu vancungmi hnenah napi in a au ih, “Na favah hmang awla leilung tlun sabit hmuanih sabit pawl hlep thlang aw; ziangahtile sabit an hmin zo a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cutiin vancungmi in a favah cu leilungah a vun hawi ih sabit hri ihsin sabit rah a hlep ih Pathian thinhengnak sabit rialnak sungah a vun thlak.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sabit rah cu khawpi lengih a ummi sabit rialnak ah an rial ih sabit rialnak sung ihsin thisen a luang; cuih thisen cu peng zahnih tiang a luang ih rang kakharh tiang a thuk."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule vanah a dang khawruahharza le a maksakmi hmuhnak ka nei lala. Vancungmi pasarih in natsia pasarih an keng; hi natsia cu a neta bik hremnak an si, ziangahtile Pathian thinhengnak a lang netnak a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule ka zoh ih meisa thawn a rawi awmi thlalang, tifinriat bangtuk a si mi ka hmu. Cuih tlunah sahrang le a lem siseh, a nambat ai-awhtu siseh, a nehtu pawl khal siseh ka hmu. Cuih nehtu pawl cu thlalang tifinriat kapah an ding ih Pathian pekmi ṭingṭang an keng.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Pathian riantu a si mi Moses ih hla le Tuufa ih hla cu hiti in an sak: “Bawipa, Ziangkimtithei Pathian, Na thiltuahmi hi ziangtluk mangbangza so an si. Miphun hmuahhmuahih Siangpahrang, Na lamzin cu ziangtluk a dingmi le a dikmi so an si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bawipa, nangmah a lo ṭihzah lotu zoso a um ding? Na maksak zia a phuang lotu zoso a um ding? Nangmah lawng na thianghlim a si. Miphun hmuahhmuah na hnenah an ra ding ih an lo bia ding. Ziangahtile a dikmi na thil tuahmi cu mi hmuahhmuah in an hmu zo.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuih hnuah vancungah a ong awmi biakinn ka hmu ih a sungah Puanthlam Thianghlim khal ka hmu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Natsia pasarih a kengtu vancungmi pasarih cuih biakinn sung ihsin an ra suak; annih tla cu a tleu zetmi puanrang thawn an thuam aw ih sui ṭaangkhap thawn an ṭaang an khap aw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule thilnung pali lakah pakhat in kumkhua in kumkhua tiang a nungmi Pathian ih thinhengnak in a khatmi sui kheng pasarih cu vancungmi pasarih hnenah a pek.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Biakinn cu Pathian huham le sunlawinak meikhu in a khat ih vancungmi pasarih in an kenmi natsia pasarih a reh hlanah cun zohman biakinn sungah an lut thei lo."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule biakinn ihsin aw ring ka thei ih vancungmi pasarih hnenah, “Feh uhla Pathian thinhengnak kheng pasarih kha leilungah vun thle uh!” tiah a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Pakhatnak vancungmi a feh ih a kheng cu leilungah a thlet. Sahrang hminsinnak a neitu le sahrang lem a biatu pawl taksa parah ṭihnungza le a na zetmi hma sia a suak.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cule vancungmi pahnihnak in a kheng cu tifinriat parah a vun thlet. Tidai cu miruak ihsin a suakmi thisen bangtuk ah a cang ih tifinriat sungih a nungmi hmuahhmuah an thi ṭheh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cule vancungmi pathumnak in a kheng cu tiva le cerhtiput parah a thlet ih tidai cu thisen ah an cang ṭheh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tidai tlunih thuneitu vancungmi in, “Hi na thuṭhennak pawl hi a dikmi an si, Maw a Thianghlimmi, atuih a ummi le hlan khalah a rak um zomi Pathian!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mithiang pawl le profet pawl thisen an suahter ruangah an in dingah thisen na pekmi hi in tlak hrimhrim an si,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Biakṭheng ihsin aw pakhat ka thei ih, “Bawipa, Ziangkimtithei Pathian! Na thu relcatmi hi a dikmi le a dingmi an si!” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule vancungmi palinak in a kheng cu ni parah a thle ih minung kang dingah thu a pek.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ni in a kang hai ruangah minung pawl in hi hremnak tlunih thuneitu Pathian ih hmin kha an camriam ciamco. Asinain an sualnak ihsin an sir lo ih Pathian khal thangṭhatnak an pe cuang lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cule vancungmi panganak in a kheng cu sahrang ih bawi tokham parah a thlet. Sahrang ih uknak khuazakip ah thimkhawzing a tlung ih minung pawl cu an tuarmi a nat tuk ruangah an lei an keu ciamco.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> An nat le an hma ruangah vancung Pathian cu an cam an riam. Asinain an thilsual tuahmi cu an sir aw cuang lo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule vancungmi paruknak in a kheng cu Eufrates tivapi parah a thlet. Tiva cu a kang ṭheh; cumicu nisuahlam ihsin a ra dingmi siangpahrang pawl hrang lamzin ongtu a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule butlak bangtuk a si mi thlarau borhhlawh pathum ka hmu. Rulhreng kaa sung le sahrang kaa sung le profet deu kaa sung ihsin a suakmi an si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cupawl cu hmuhsaknak mak a tuahtu khawsia thlarau an si. Cuih thlarau pathum cu an feh ih leilung tlun siangpahrang hmuahhmuah hmun khatah an hruai khawm. Cutiih an hruai khawmnak cu Ziangkimtithei Pathian ih Ni sunglawi ni ah raldo dingah a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Zohhnik! Fifir bangin ka ra ding. Misenpi hmaiah taklawng le ningzakih an um lonak dingah itthat lotein a meng ih a hnipuan a fingkhawitu cu mi lungawi an si,” tiah Bawipa in a ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule thlarau pathum in siangpahrang pawl cu Hebru ṭong in Armageddon an timi hmunah an hruai khawm.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule vancungmi pasarihnak in a kheng cu thli lakah a thlet ih Siangpahrang tokham umnak biakinn sung ihsin aw pakhat a ra thang ih, “A cem zo,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutikah nimthla a kau zukzo, khua a ri durdo, ṭeek a tla ciamco ih tuksumza ling a hnin. Minung um hramthok ihsin cubangtuk linghnin a um dah lo. Linghnin hmuahhmuah lakah a besia bikmi a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Khawpi tumzet cu ṭhenthum ah a kuai ih ram dangih khawpi hmuahhmuah khal a siatsuah ṭheh. Pathian in a nasami Babilon cu a hngilh loih a khuathaiih a thinhengnak sabitti a inter.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tikulh hmuahhmuah an hlo ih tlang hmuahhmuah an cemral ṭheh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Rial tum zetzet, pakhat ah pawng zakhat tiang a ritmi rial van ihsin minung parah an tla. Cutiin hremnak an tuar ruangah mi in Pathian an cam an riam, ziangahtile an tuarmi natsia cu tuksumza a si."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule kheng pasarih a kengtu vancungmi pasarih lakih pakhat ka hnenah a ra ih, “Ra awla tiva tampi kiangih toh-mi khawpi, hminthang hlawhhlangnu khi ziangvekin hremnak a tong ding, ti ka lo hmuh ding.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Leilung tlun siangpahrang pawl amah thawn nupa sualnak an tuah ih leilungtlun mi pawl khal in amah ih tisa diriam sualnak sabitti an in ruangah an ri ṭheh a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Thlarau in i zeel ih vancungmi in hramlakah i feh pi. Cutawkah sahrang sen parah nunau pakhat a to ka hmu; cuih sahrang taksa pumpuluk ah Pathian hmuhsuamnak hmin tampi an ngan ih cuih sahrang cu lu pasarih le ki pahra a nei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuih nunau cu mepian sen le puansen dup in a thuam aw ih hlawnthil sui le tikep lung le lungmankhung dangdang in a taksa cu a khat ṭheh. A kut in sui khuathai pakhat a keng ih cuih khuathai cu a tisa diriam sualnak thil zoh mawi lo le fihnungza thil in a khat.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A cal ah hmin pakhat an ngan ih tican thup a nei. “A maksak zetmi Babilon, hlawhhlang hmuahhmuah le misual borhhlawh hmuahhmuah ih nu,” ti a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule cuih nunau cu Pathian mithiang pawl ih thisen le Jesuh an rinsan ruangih thah a tuartu pawl ih thisen a in ruangah a ri, ti ka hmu. Cuih nunau ka hmuh tikah ka mang a bang ngaingai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutikah vancungmi pakhat in, “Ziangah so na mang a bang? Nunau ih tican thup le nunau nu a tonak sahrang lu pasarih le ki pahra a nei mi sahrang ih tican thup cu ka lo sim ding.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hi na hmuhmi sahrang hi a rak nung dah naón atu cu a nung nawn lo; tawpneilo khur sung ihsin a hung suak ding ih siatralnak ah a feh lan ding. Leilung siam hlan ihsin nunnak cabu sungih hmin ngan lomi pawl in cuih sahrang an zoh tikah an mang a bang ngaingai ding. A rak nung dah naón atu cu a nung nawn lo; asinain a hung suak sal ding.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Fimnak le theihnak neih a ṭul. Lu pasarih cu nunau a tonak tlang pasarih an si. Siangpahrang pasarih khal an si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuih siangpahrang pasarih lakah panga cu an tlu zo; pakhat in a uk lai; a dang pakhat cu a ra hrih lo. A rat tikah tikcu tawite sung lawng a uk ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A rak nung dah naón atu-ah a nung nawn lomi sahrang cu siangpahrang pariatnak a si; siangpahrang pasarih lakih a telmi a si ih siatralnak ih a thleng dingmi a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Ki pahra na hmuhmi cu ram a uk thok hrih lotu siangpahrang pahra an si; asinain annih cu sahrang thawn nazi pakhat sung uk dingah thuneihnak pek an si ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> An pahra in an huham le an thuneihnak cu sahrang hnenih pe ding cu an tumtah ciarmi a si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Annih cu Tuufa an do ding; sikhalsehla Tuufa le amah ih a kawhmi, a hrilmi le amah a rinsantu pawl in an neh ding, ziangahtile Tuufa cu bawi hmuahhmuah lakih Bawi bik, siangpahrang hmuahhmuah lakih Siangpahrang sin a si,” tiin i sim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule vancungmi in, “Hlawhhlang nu ih tonak tidai na hmuhmi cu miphun kip, hrin kip, ram kip le ṭong kip an si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na hmuhmi ki pahra le sahrang in hlawhhlang nu cu an hua ding; a neihmi thil hmuahhmuah an long ding ih a taklawngin an taan ding; a sa an ei ding ih meisa in an ur ding.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Pathian tumtahmi an tuahsuaknak dingah Pathian in an thinlung sungah tuah duhnak thinlung a ret. Curuangah thinlung rualtein hna an ṭuan tlang ih Pathian thu a kim hlan sung an ram uknak huham cu sahrang hnenah an pek.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Na hmuhmi nunau cu leilung tlun siangpahrang pawl a uktu khawpi tumpi a si,” tiah i ti."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hi hnuah vancungmi pakhat vancung ihsin a rung ṭum ka hmu. Amah cu thuneihnak huham tumzet a nei ih a tleunak in leilung pumpuluk a vangter ṭheh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ring zetin a au ih, “Nunau nu a tlu zo! Babilon maksak cu a siat zo! Khawsia le thlarau borhhlawh in an luah ih a sungah fihnungza le mitkemza vate a phunphun in an khat.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ziangahtile miphun hmuahhmuah in a taksa hiar sualnak zu an in ih an ri ṭheh. Siangpahrang pawl thawn tisa sualnak an tuah ih sumtuahtu pawl khal supnak nei lo a taksa hiar nomnak thawngin milian ah an cang,” tiah a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cule aw dang pakhat vancung ihsin ka thei ih, “Ra suak uh, ka minung pawl, Kha nu hnen ihsin ra suak uh. A sualnak sungah tel hlah uh, Hrem a tuarnak sung khalah tel hlah uh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ziangahtile a sualnak cu van a tiang ih, A ṭhatlonak cu Pathian in a ciing ringring a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nanmah a lo tuah vek cekci-in a parah tuah ve uh. A tuahmi let hnih in phulei sam uh. Nan in dingih a rawimi hnakih let hnih cak in a in dingah a khuathai sungah rawi sak uh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sunlawinak le nunnomnak amah le amah a rak pek awk zat in, natnak le riahsiatnak pe ve uh. Ziangahtile a thinlungte in, ‘Hinah ka to, siangpahrang bawinu ka si, nuhmei ka si lo, riahsiatnak ka tong dah lo ding,’ a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hi vek a si ruangah ni khat sungah rinlopi in pulhnat in a tlun ding. Natnak, riahsiatnak le paampi a tong ding. Meisa ih ur a tong ding. Ziangahtile a thuṭhentu Bawipa Pathian cu Ziangkimtithei a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A tisa sualnak le a taksa hiar nomnak sungih a teltu leilung siangpahrang pawl in Babilon khawpi meisa ih a kangnak meikhu an hmuh tikah an ṭap an ai ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cutiih a tuarnak an hmuh tikah tuar ve pang ding an ṭih ruangah hlavaang ah an ding ih, “Ziangtluk ṭihnungza so a si! Ziang tluk tuksumza so a si! Khua maksak le a cakmi Babilon khawlipi! Nazi pakhat sungah hremsiatnak na ton hi!” tiah an ti ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Leilung tlun sumtuah pawl khal cu nu hremsiatnak a ton cu an ninghanpi ih an ṭap, ziangahtile zohman in an thilri an lei nawn lo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Zohman in an sui, an ngun, an lungmankhung, an tikep lungmankhung le patzai in tahmi puanrang, mepian sendup puan, pu puan, puan sen le a ngah har zetmi thing ihsin tuah mi a phunphun, vuiho le thing mankhung ihsin tuahmi a phunphun, daar, thir, lungrang le,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> thinghawng hmui, masala, rimhmui, mura rimhmui, frankinsens rimhmui le sabitti le hriak, vainim le sangvut, caw le tuu, rang le rangleng, sal le minung khal zohman in an lei nawn lo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sumtuah pawl in cu nuih hnenah, “Nei ningla tiih saduh na thahmi thil ṭha hmuahhmuah an hloral ṭheh zo; na lennak le na sunlawinak kha an cem thluh zo ih ziangtik hmanah na ngah sal nawn lo ding,” an ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cutawk khawpi sungah sumtuah tahratih a lianmi pawl in a tuarnak sungih tel ve pang ding an ṭih ruangah hlatzet ah an ding ding. An riahsia in an ṭap ding ih,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “ṭihnungza a si! Tuksumza a si! Babilon khawlipi cu! Patzai in tahmi puanrang, sendup puan le puan sen in a rak thuam aw ṭheu ih sui hlawnthil le lungmankhung le tikep lungmankhung in a cei-aw ṭheu a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Asinain nazi pakhat sungah a hlawnthil hmuahhmuah cu a cemral ṭheh a si,” an ti ding. Tangphawlawng mawngtu bawi pawl le lawng a totu mi hmuahhmuah, lawng hnaṭuan pawl le tidai parih pumcawmnak a hawltu hmuahhmuah hlapi ah an ding ih,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> khawpi a kangnak meikhu an hmuh tikah, “Hi khawlipi bangtuk khawpi ziangtik hmanah a um dah lo,” tiah an au.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> An lu ah leivut phulh aw in an ṭap an raak ih, “ṭihnungza le tuksumza a va si so, hi khawpi hrangah cun! Tangphawlawng a nei ih ti parah sum a tuahtu hmuahhmuah cu hi nunau ih lennak thawngin milian ih an cannak khawpi a si. Asinain nazi pakhat sungah a neihmi hmuahhmuah a cemfai ṭheh a si!” an ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Maw van, Babilon a siatral ruangah na lungawi aw! Maw Pathian mithiang pawl, tirhthlah pawl le profet pawl, lungawi aipuang in um uh! Ziangahtile nan parih a thiltuahmi ruangah Pathian hnen ihsin cawhkuan a tong zo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cule a cak zetmi vancungmi pakhat in lungto pakhat, fang rialnak lungtlep tumpi tia khi a khai ih tifinriat sungah a vun hlon ih, “Hi bangtuk in Babilon khawlipi cu vuakthlakmi bangin hlon a si ding ih zohman in an hmu sal nawn lo ding.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Babilon khawlipi ṭingṭang tum thawng le minung awzai, phirivau tum thiam pawl in phirivau an tum thawng le tawtawrawt tum thiam pawl ih an tawtawrawt tum thawng cu na sungah a thang nawn lo ding. Ziangbangtuk hnaṭuan a si khalle hnaṭuantu na sungah an um nawn lo ding. Fang rial awn thawng na thei nawn lo ding.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ziangtik hmanah na sungah mei-inn a vang nawn lo ding. Nupi ṭhi tlangval aw siseh mothar aw siseh na sungah a leng nawn lo ding. Na sungih sumtuahtu pawl cu leilung tlunah huham nei bik an si, sikhalsehla na dawithiamnak in leilungtlun mi hmuahhmuah cu na bum ṭheh a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Profet le Pathian mithiang pawl ih thisen a sungih a luan ruangah Babilon cu hrem a tong zo. A si, leilung tlunih thah a tuartu pawl ih thisen cu hi khawsungah a luang a si."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih hnuah vancungah mi tampi-ih aw bangtuk ka thei ih, “Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh! Rundamnak le sunlawinak le huham cu kan Pathian ih ta an si!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A thuṭhennak cu a dik le a dingmi an si. Hlawhhlang nu, a taksa hiar sualnak thawn leilung a balhtertu cu hrem a si zo. Pathian riantu pawl a thah ruangah amah cu Pathian in a hremsuak zo a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cule ringzet in, “Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh! Khawlipi a kang ruangih meikhu cu kumkhua in vanah a kai a si,” tiah an au lala.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cutikah upa kul hluanli le thilnung pali cu an bok ih bawi tokham parih a totu Pathian cu an biak. Annih in, “Amen! Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh,” tiah an ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule bawi tokham ihsin aw pakhat a ra thang ih, “Kan Pathian cu thangṭhat uh; a riantu pawl le a minung pawl, a tum a te ti loin amah a ṭihzahtu hmuahhmuah in thangṭhat uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cuih hnuah miburpi ih aw bangtuk, a hrual in a hrual awmi tisuar aw bangtuk, khua a ri durdomi aw bangtuk ka thei. Cuih aw in, “Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh! Ziangahtile Bawipa, Ziangkimtithei kan Pathian cu Siangpahrang a si!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Lungawi aipuang in um uhsi! A maksaknak cu thangṭhat uhsi! Ziangahtile Tuufa nupi ṭhit caan a thleng zo ih monu khal ṭhit awknak puai hrangah timtuah ciain a um zo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A hruk dingah patzai in tahmi puanrang a tleu zetmi cu pek a si zo,” tiah an ti ka thei. Cuih patzai ih tahmi puanrang cu Pathian minung pawl ih thilṭha tuahmi a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Vancungmi in, “Himi hi ngan aw: Tuufa nupi ṭhit puai ih sawmmi pawl cu mi lungawi an si. Hi thu hi Pathian thudik a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cutikah amah biak dingah a kehramah ka bok, asinain anih in, “Khatiin bok hlah! Kei khal nangmah bangtuk siahhlawh ka si ve; Jesuh in a phuanmi thutak a pomhngettu nan unau lakah pakhat ka si ve. Pathian lawng biak ding a si,” tiah a ti. Jesuh ih a phuanmi thutak hi a si profet pawl thinlung a thotertu cu!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule vancung khi a ong aw ka hmu ih rang raang pakhat a lang. A parih a totu cu Rintlak le Midik tiah kawhmi a si. Thu a ṭhen tikah le ral a do tikah dingnak thawn a ṭhen ih a do a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A mit tla cu meisa bangtuk in a alh ih a lu parah bawi lukhuh tampi a khum. A parah a hmin ngan ciain a um, asinain amah siar lo zohman in cuih hmin cu an thei lo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A hnipuan hrukmi cu thisen sungih hnimmi a si. A hmin cu, “Pathian Thu,” ti a si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Vancung ralkap pawl in patzai ih tahmi puanrang thiang hruk in le rang raang parah to tahratin amah cu an thlun.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A kaa sung ihsin a hriam zetmi ralnam pakhat a ra suak ih cumi thawn miphun tampi a neh ding. Thirfung thawn a uk ding ih Ziangkimtithei Pathian thinhengnak cu sabit rialnak sungih sabit an pal bangin a pal ding.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> A puan parah le a kawng ah hmin an ngan ih, “Siangpahrang hmuahhmuah lakih Siangpahrang sin, bawi hmuahhmuah lakih Bawi bik,” ti a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule vancungmi pakhat ni parih a din kha ka hmu. Van ih a zammi vate hnenah aw ring zetin a au ih, “Pathian ih puai tumpi a tuah dingmi kha ra zawh khawm uh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ra uhla siangpahrang pawl, ralkap hotu bawi pawl, ralkap pawl, rang le rang totu pawl, mi hmuahhmuah, sal siseh miluat siseh, mitum siseh mite siseh, cu pawl ih sa ra ei uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cule sahrang le leilung tlun siangpahrang pawl le an ralkap pawl cu rang parih a totu le a ralkap pawl do dingah hmun khatah an khawm aw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sahrang cu an kai ih a mithmuh ah hmuhsaknak mak tampi a tuahtu profet deu khal an kaih cih. Cuih khawruahhar a tuahnak in sahrang hminsinnak a kengtu le sahrang lem a biatu pawl cu a bum. Sahrang le profet deu cu hmun khatah kaatmei thawn a alh ringringmi meilipi sungah an nungcung in an hlon.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> An ralkap pawl cu rang parih a totu pa ih kaa sung ihsin a suakmi ralnam in an that. Cule an sa cu vate hmuahhmuah in an ei thei zat in an ei."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule vancung ihsin vancungmi pakhat a rung ṭum ih a kut in tawpneilo khur onnak tawhfung le a rit zetmi thir cikcin a ken kha ka hmu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cuih vancungmi in khua hlanlai ihsin rulpi a si mi rulhreng cu a kaih ih thir cikcin in a khit ih tawpneilo khur ahcun kum thawngkhat sung a thlak. Cuih rulhreng cu Khawsia a si lole Satan timi cu a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kum thawngkhat a kim hlanah cun zohman bum nawn hlah seh tiah cuih khur sungah cun tawh a hren ih hminsinnak tacik a khen cih. Cuih hnuah caan malte sung thlah sal a si ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cule bawi tokham pawl le a parih a totu, thuṭhen theinak an hnenih pek a si mi pawl ka hmu. Jesuh ih a phuanmi thutak le Pathian thu an phuan ruangih thah a tuartu pawl ih thlarau pawl ka hmu. Annih pawl cun sahrang an bia lo, a lem khal an bia lo; sahrang ih hminsinnak cu an cal ah siseh an baan ah siseh an nei lo. An nung sal ih siangpahrang tokham parah to in Khrih thawn kum thawngkhat sung an uk.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A dang mithi pawl cu kum thawngkhat a cem hlanah cun an thosal hrih lo. Himi hi mithi thawhsalnak hmaisa bik a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hi bangtuk in mithi thawhsalnak a hmaisa bikih a teltu cu mi lungawi le mi thluasuak an si. Voihnih thihnak in an tlunah thu a nei nawn lo. Pathian le Khrih hrangah puithiam an ṭuan ding ih amah thawn kum thawngkhat sung an uk ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kum thawngkhat hnuah Satan cu a thawng tlaknak ihsin suah a si ding ih,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> leilung tlun khuazakipah ṭeekdarhmi miphun pawl bum dingah a feh ding; cuih miphun pawl cu Gog le Magog ti an si. Raldo dingah Satan in hmunkhatah a finkhawm ding; anmah cu tifinriat kapih vunnel zat an si ding.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Leilung tlun khuazakipah an feh ih Pathian minung pawl umnak hmun le a duh zetmi khawpi kha an kulh ṭheh. Asinain van ihsin meisa a rung tla ih a kang that ṭheh hai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cule anmah bumtu Satan cu sahrang le profet deu an hlonnak, kaat meilipi sungah an hlon. Cutawkah a sun a zanin hrem ringring an si ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule a maksak zetmi bawi tokham raang le a parih a totu ka hmu. Bawi tokham parih a totu mithmuh ihsin van le leilung cu an tlan ih hmuh theih an si nawn lo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A thi ciami pawl cu a tum a sen in bawi tokham hmaiah an ding ka hmu. Cabu pawl an kau; cuih hnuah nunnak cabu timi cabu dang pakhat an kau lala. Mithi pawl cu cuih cabu sungih an rak khum ciami an hnaṭuan vekin an thu ṭhen a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule tifinriat in a sungih ummi mithi pawl a hun suah. Thihnak le mithi khua khal in an hren cihmi mithi pawl an hun suah ve. An zatein an hnaṭuan ciami vekin thuṭhen an si ṭheh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule thihnak le mithi khua cu tilipi vek a si mi meilipi sungah thlak an si. Hi meilipi cu voihnih thihnak kha a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Zokhal nunnak cabu sungih hmin ngan lomi cu meilipi sungah hlon an si."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih hnuah van thar le lei thar ka hmu. A hmaisa ih a rak ummi van le leilung kha cu an hlota ih tifinriat khal a um nawn lo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule Khawpi Thianghlim Jerusalem thar cu, a pasal dingmi tong dingah cei-aw in a timtuah awmi monu vekin Pathian hnen vancung ihsin a rung ṭum kha ka hmu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bawi tokham ihsin aw ringzet ka thei ih, “Pathian umnak inn cu minung hnenah a si zo. Amah cu an hnenah a um ding ih annih tla cu amah ih minung an si ding. Pathian Amah rori an hnenah a um ding ih an Pathian a si ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> An mitthli hmuahhmuah a hnul sak ding. Thih a um nawn lo ding; ninghang riahsiat, aihram ṭahnak le natnak a um nawn lo ding. Ziangahtile thil hlun pawl cu an hlo ṭheh zo,” tiah a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule bawi tokham parih a totu in, “Zohhnik uh, thil hmuahhmuah a thar in ka tuah a si,” tiah a ti. Ka hnenah, “Himi thu hi ngan aw, ziangahtile a dikmi le zumtlak thu a si,” tiah i ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule, “Ziangkim ṭheh thluh a si zo. Keimah cu Alfa le Omega ka si, a thawhnak le a cemnetnak ka si. Zokhal ti a haaltu cu nunnak cerhti in dingah man loin ka pe ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nehtu hmuahhmuah in himi hi an co ding. An Pathian ka si ding ih annih cu ka faale an si ding.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sikhalsehla ṭihhrutmi, zumnak bansantu, fihnungza tuahtu, mi a that hrimtu, nupa sualnak a tuahtu, dawithiam pawl, milem a biatu le thuphanpertu pawl ih umnak ding hmun cu kaat meilipi sungah a si ding ih cumi cu voihnih thihnak a si,” tiah i ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Vancungmi pasarih lakih a neta bik, natsia pasarih in a khatmi kheng pasarih a kengtu in ka hnenah, “Ra aw, Tuufa ih nupi ding Mo cu ka lo hmuh ding,” tiah i ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Thlarau in i zeel ih vancungmi in a saang zetmi tlang parah i fehpi. Cule Jerusalem, Khawpi Thianghlim cu Pathian hnen vancung in a rung ṭum kha i hmuh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Pathian sunlawinak thawn a tleumi Khawpi a si; Jasper timi lunghring mankhung bangin a tleu ih thlalang bangin a fai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A kimvel in a saang zetmi phar in an kulh ih kotka hleihnih a nei; cuih kotka cu vancungmi hleihnih in an kil. Cuih kotka ahcun Israel miphun hleihnih ih hmin an ngan.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Siir khatah kotka pathum fingfing an um: nisuahnak lamah pathum, thlanglam ah pathum, saklam ah pathum le nitlaknak lamah pathum an um.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Khawpi kulhnak phar cu inn-hramṭohnak lungto hleihnih parih phunmi a si; cuih lungto parah cun Tuufa ih tirhthlah hleihnih pawl ih hmin an ngan.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka hnenah i simtu vancungmi in khawpi le a phar le a kotka pawl tahnak ah sui tahfung a keng.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Khawpi cu a kauhlam le a saulam le a saanlam a bangaw ṭheh. Vancungmi in a tahfung thawn cuih khawpi cu a tah: a saulam peng thawngkhat le zanga, a kauhlam peng thawngkhat le zanga a si ih a saanlam khal peng thawngkhat le zanga thotho a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Vancungmi in milai ih tahfung thawn phar khal a tah ih pi zahnih le hleiruk a saang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Phar cu Jasper timi lunghring mankhung in an tuah ih khawpi cu thlalang bangin a fai mi sui hlir in tuahmi a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Khawpi hramṭohnak lungto cu lungmankhung a phunphun in mawitermi a si. A pakhatnak cu jasper timi lunghring mankhung a si, a pahnihnak cu safaira timi mepian lungmankhung a si, a pathumnak cu agate timi hring-eu lungmankhung a si, a palinak cu emerald timi hringdup lungmankhung a si;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> a panganak cu onix timi lungsen mankhung a si, a paruknak cu karnelian timi a sendupmi lungmankhung a si, a pasarihnak cu aihre le sui pianzia rawimi quartz lungmankhung a si, a pariatnak cu beriil timi mepian le a hring rawimi lungmankhung a si, a pakuanak cu topaz timi aihre lungmankhung a si, a pahranak cu khalsidoni timi a pawlmi lungmankhung a si, hleikhatnak cu turquoise timi a sen le aihre rawimi lungmankhung a si ih hleihnihnak cu amethyst timi a eengmi lungmankhung a si.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kotka hleihnih cu tikep lungmankhung hleihnih in tuahmi an si; kotka ih kipin tikep lungmankhung pakhat fingfingih tuahmi an si. Khawpi lamzin cu sui hlir in tuahmi a si ih thlalang bangin a fai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cuih khawpi ah biakinn a um lo, ziangahtile a biakinn cu Ziangkimtithei Bawipa Pathian le Tuufa a si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ni le thlapi ih tleunak khal a ṭul lo, ziangahtile Pathian sunlawinak cu cuih khawpi ah a tleu ih an mei-inn cu Tuufa a si.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Leilung tlun mi hmuahhmuah in cuih khawpi tleunak thawngin fehnak an hmu ding ih leilung tlun siangpahrang pawl in cuih khawpi sungah an lennak sumsaw an keng ding.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cuih khawpi kotka pawl cu sun nihlawh in on an si ding; ziangtik hmanah an khar lo ding, ziangahtile cutawkah zan a um nawn lo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Leilung miphun hmuahhmuah in an phun lennak le sunlawinak cu cuih khawpi ah an rak keng ciar ding.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Sikhalsehla cuih khawpi sungah a thiang lomi zianghman a lut lo ding; ningsinza thil a tuahtu le thuphanpertu khal an lut lo ding. Tuufa nunnak cabu sungih hmin nganmi lawng an lut ding."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule cuih vancungmi cun thlalang bangin a tleumi nunnak tiva i hmuh. Cuih tiva cu Pathian le Tuufa ih bawi tokham ihsin a puut ih,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> khawpi lamzin laifang in a luang. Cuih tiva kap hnih ah nunnak thingkung a um ih thla khat voikhat in kum khatah voihleihnih an rah. Cule thinghnah cu mi phunkip hrangah damnak a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Pathian ih camsiat a tongtu zianghman cuih khawpi sungah a um thei lo ding. Pathian le Tuufa ih bawi tokham cu cuih khawpi ah a um ding ih a siahhlawh pawl in amah cu an biak ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hmaiton in an hmu aw ding ih a hmin cu an cal ah ngan a si ding.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuih hmunah zan a um nawn lo ding; mei-inn siseh nitleu siseh an ṭul lo ding, ziangahtile Bawipa Pathian cu an tleunak a si ding ih siangpahrang bangin kumkhua in an uk lanta ding.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule vancungmi in ka hnenah, “Hi thu pawl hi a dikmi le zumtlak an si. Profet pawl hnenah a Thlarau a thlahtu Bawipa Pathian in a thleng cing dingmi thil kha Amah ih siahhlawh pawl theihter dingah a vancungmi a thlah a si,” tiah i ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Jesuh in, “Ngai uh, ka ra cing ding. Hi cabu sungih nganmi profet ṭongkam a thluntu cu mi lungawi an si,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Keimah Johan in hipawl hi ka hmu ih ka thei. Cutiin ka hmu ih ka theih hnuah hi bangtuk thil i hmuhtu vancungmi ih kehramah ka bok ih a biak ka tum.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Asinain anih in, “I bia hlah! Kei khal nangmah le na unau profet pawl le hi cabu sungih nganmi thu a thluntu pawl bangtuk in Pathian ih siahhlawh ka si ve! Pathian bia sawn aw!” tiah i ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cule ka hnenah, “Hi cabu sungih nganmi profet ṭongkam hi thup hlah, ziangahtile hi thu pawl hi a kim cing ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Zokhal thil ṭha lo a tuahtu cu tuah hrih ko seh; fihnungza a si mi cu fihnungza in nung hrih ko seh; thil ṭha a tuahtu cu tuah hrih ko seh; cule a thianghlimmi cu thianghlim in um hrih ko seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Jesuh in, “Ngai uh! Ka ra cing ding! An hnaṭuan vekih pe ciar dingah ṭuanman ka rak keng ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Keimah cu Alfa le Omega, a hmaisa bik le a neta bik, a thawhnak le a cemnetnak ka si,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> An hnipuan fai zetin an sawp ih nunnak thingkungih rah ei theinak thu le khawpi sungah kotka ihsin luh theinak thu a neitu cu mi lungawi an si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sikhalsehla uico bangtuk in a nungmi, dawithiam pawl, nupa sualnak a tuahtu, mi a thattu pawl, milem a biatu pawl le an ṭong in siseh, an tuahnak in siseh, thuphanper pawl cu khawpi lengah an um ding.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Keimah Jesuh in hi thu hi kawhhran pawl hnenih than dingah ka vancungmi nan hnenah ka run thlah. Keimah hi David ih hram le tesinfa ka si; keimah hi deirel arsi tleu ka si,” tiah a ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Thlarau le Mo cun, “Ra aw,” an ti. Hi thu a theitu hmuahhmuah in, “Ra aw,” tiah ti ciar hai seh. Tihal mi hmuahhmuah in ra uh; nunnak tidai a duhtu hmuahhmuah in man loin ra in uh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Keimah Johan in, hi cabu sungih nganmi profet ṭongkam a theitu hmuahhmuah hnenah, ralrinnak ka lo pek; hi profet ṭongkam tlunah zokhal thudang a bettu cu Pathian in a parah hi cabu sungih nganmi natsia hremnak kha a bet ve ding.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cule zokhal hi cabu sungih profet ṭongkam nganmi hi a phiat hlotu cu hi cabu sungih ngan ciami a co dingmi nunnak thingrah le Khawpi Thianghlim sungih luh theinak a co dingmi kha Pathian in a phiat hlosak ve ding.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hi thu hmuahhmuah a phuangtu in, “A si! Ka ra cing ding,” tiah a ti. Amen! Bawipa Jesuh, ra thlang aw!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bawipa Jesuh ih zaangfahnak cu nan zate hnenah um hram seh."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;